title: ThoSeism
author: TheLilKato
pages:
#- ThoSeism is about the acceptance of all no mattar where they hail from nor the gender of fellow being.
Lists of Gods:
 Ikeus, God of Trade
Fyldite, God of Fortune
Vantos, God of Hope
Xymir, God of Science
Mycthar, God of the Dark

#- Zaptyx, God of Life & Death
Sistus, God of Death
Adon, God of Loyalty
Areus, God of Fame
Koteus, God of Abundance 

Accept all
Kill the ones that oppose us.
